mods.name: Alternative Textures
mods.instructions:
Alternative Textures (Included Framework)

Alternative Textures enables texture variation for nearly any placeable object in Stardew Valley!
Purchase a Paint Bucket (and other tools0 from Robin. You can use the Paint Bucket tool to adjust the textures of wallpaper, flooring, fences, furniture, craftables, buildings... just about anything!

mods.instructions:
Recommended map for Aesthetic Valley | Witchcore is "Grandpa's Farm", which will replace the default (first) farm in-game while enabled.

Grandpa's Farm is wonderful for for solo playthrough because it is a little more compact and therefore easier to manage.

If you install multiple farms, you will want to disable any farm you are not using. Press Skip if you would rather not download this farm.
